      "title": "The emergency law is passed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The gazette announcement of the imposition of emergency law issued by the President was passed in Parliament today (27) afternoon by 57 majority votes.",
        "120 votes were received in favor of the announcement and only 63 votes were received against it.",
        "The debate regarding the announcement of the emergency law was held throughout the day yesterday."
      ],
